ideo backgrounds, add stunning parallax effects to your content, cool section borders, custom colors, setup element design presets or custom queries with no coding skills required, only using the visual drag\'n drop interface.[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"22811\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Premium Sliders\" icon=\"icon icon-image\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Premium Sliders[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna Ships with a FREE license of the amazing [tooltip title=\"Visit Plugin\'s Page\"]<strong>Revolutions Slider</strong>[/tooltip] plugin (<strong>$18 Value</strong>) which lets you create stunning animated sliders with its full featured drag\'n drop backend that is very easy to use.[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"22810\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"large\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna also utilizes fully Responsive, draggable Image sliders and carousels that you can easily use via the Visual composer interface in order to create stunning looking Image sliders, post carousels, portfolio carousels, logo carousels and testimonial carousels.[/vc_column_text][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Theme Options\" icon=\"icon icon-cog\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Rich Theme Options[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna comes with a vast variety of customizable Theme Options that help you setup websites with unique look &amp; feel. You can setup most of them globally for your website in the Theme Options panel then you can modify some of them on a per page basis under your page editor. An extended version of the Wordpress Customize screen is also available where you can preview some of the global settings Live on your website as you make the changes. Here’s a list of the global Theme Options offered in Fortuna:[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22814\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_row_inner el_id=\"\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<ul>\n	<li>Logo</li>\n	<li>Retina Logo</li>\n	<li>Favicon</li>\n	<li>Header Height</li>\n	<li>Sticky Header Toggle</li>\n	<li>Sticky Header Height</li>\n	<li>Sticky Header Background</li>\n	<li>Sticky Header Opacity</li>\n	<li>Main Menu Text Color</li>\n	<li>Main Menu Hover Text Color</li>\n	<li>Main Menu Animated Underline Effect</li>\n	<li>Main Menu Underline Effect Color</li>\n	<li>Main Menu Block Style Toggle</li>\n	<li>Sub-Menu Arrow Animation on Hover</li>\n	<li>Search Field in the Header</li>\n	<li>Search Field Separator</li>\n	<li>Mega Menu Bordered Columns</li>\n	<li>Subheader Section in Header</li>\n	<li>Hide Subheader on Scroll for Sticky Header</li>\n	<li>Header Contact Email</li>\n	<li>Header Contact Phone</li>\n	<li>Header Contact Position Toggle</li>\n	<li>Header Social Icons (10)</li>\n	<li>Transparent Header Logo</li>\n	<li>Transparent Logo Transition Effect</li>\n	<li>Transparent Header Background Color</li>\n	<li>Transparent Header Opacity</li>\n	<li>Transparent Header Navigation Text Color</li>\n	<li>Transparent Header Navigation Hover Color</li>\n	<li>Enable breadcrumbs</li>\n	<li>Breadcrumb Position Toggle</li>\n	<li>Image Edges (Square/Rounded)</li>\n	<li>Footer Background (Dark/Light)</li>\n	<li>Footer Columns (1-4)</li>\n	<li>Unfolding Footer Feature Toggle</li>\n	<li>Copyrights Text in Footer</li>\n	<li>Footer Social Icons</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<ul>\n	<li>Main Navigation Font</li>\n	<li>Main Sub-Navigation Font</li>\n	<li>Heading Font</li>\n	<li>Body Font</li>\n	<li>Button Font</li>\n	<li>Wrapper Style (Full or Boxed)</li>\n	<li>Global Background Color/Image</li>\n	<li>Enable Responsive Design Toggle</li>\n	<li>Enable Retina Support Toggle</li>\n	<li>Smooth Scroll Toggle</li>\n	<li>Page Heading Style Picker</li>\n	<li>Page Heading White Text Color</li>\n	<li>Image Cropping</li>\n	<li>Default Portfolio Preset Style</li>\n	<li>Default Portfolio Hover Effect</li>\n	<li>Portfolio Item Order Clause</li>\n	<li>Portfolio Item OrderBy Clause</li>\n	<li>Portfolio Item Spacing</li>\n	<li>Enable Related Projects in Portfolio</li>\n	<li>Portfolio Items per Page</li>\n	<li>Show Full Post Content</li>\n	<li>Featured Images size on Blog Page</li>\n	<li>\"Read More\" Link Style</li>\n	<li>Default Page Sidebar Layout</li>\n	<li>Default Post Sidebar Layout</li>\n	<li>Create Sidebars (Unlimited)</li>\n	<li>Google Maps Address</li>\n	<li>Google Map Color Scheme</li>\n	<li>Google Maps Zoom Option</li>\n	<li>WooCommerce layout</li>\n	<li>Single Product Page layout</li>\n	<li>Products per Page</li>\n	<li>Enable Shopping Cart in Header</li>\n	<li>Shopping Cart in Header Color</li>\n	<li>Custom CSS</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][boc_spacing height=\"40px\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h3\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Page-specific options[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Apart from the Global Theme Options that Fortuna offers you can further customize your pages by using the \"Fortuna Page Settings\" once you are in the Page editing screen. You can thus overwrite global settings like selecting a specific sidebar, a different page background image or activating the Transparent Main Navigation only for a particular page. Here\'s a list of the available Page Setting options:\n\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\n<ul>\n	<li>Page Wrapper Style (Boxed or Full)</li>\n	<li>Show Page Heading (Area with Page Title &amp; Breadcrumbs)</li>\n	<li>Page Content Top Margin Toggle</li>\n	<li>Activate Transparent Header</li>\n	<li>Set Explicit Page Background</li>\n	<li>Select Sidebar Layout(Left/Right/None)</li>\n	<li>Pick a sidebar if Layout has one</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][boc_spacing height=\"40px\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h3\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Extended Customize Screen[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna offers an extended Customize Screen functionality where you can preview LIVE some of the changes you apply to your Global Theme Settings.\n\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner el_id=\"\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\n<ul>\n	<li>Main Theme Color (<strong>Unlimited</strong>)</li>\n	<li>Main Menu Style (<strong>6 Presets</strong> Available)</li>\n	<li>Main Menu Accent Color (<strong>Unlimited</strong>)</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Custom Headers\" icon=\"icon icon-screen\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Custom Headers, Menus, Page Headings &amp; Footers[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna provides full control of your header &amp; footer style. You can modify your <strong>header height</strong>, <strong>background color</strong>, <strong>transparency</strong>, <strong>menu color</strong>, <strong>hover menu color</strong>, pick <strong>custom fonts</strong> for your main navigation &amp; subnavigation, pick from <strong>6 different menu style presets</strong>, add an <strong>underline hover animation effect</strong> for your top level navigation items, add an <strong>animated arrow hover effect</strong> for your subnavigation items, setup transparent headers on a per page basis, set the <strong>transparency level</strong> of your transparent header as well as its <strong>background color</strong>, toggle your <strong>Sticky Header</strong> option, you can create <strong>Mega Menus</strong>, add <strong>buttons</strong> to your main navigations and many more. You can also pick your <strong>footer style</strong> as well as select how many <strong>widget columns</strong> you want in it. Menu headings (the area that contains your breadcrumbs and Page title) can also be modified on a per page basis - you can pick <strong>custom backgrounds</strong> for it, switch off the <strong>breadcrumbs</strong>, pick <strong>breadcrumb style</strong> etc. See just a few examples of customized headers (footer) below.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"40px\"][boc_img_gallery columns=\"2\" spacing=\"big_spacing\" fixed_size=\"\" img_link=\"lightbox\" show_hover_overlay=\"yes\" show_img_title=\"\" show_img_alt=\"\" image_ids=\"22818,22820,22821,22822,22823,22819,22816,22817\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Unlimited Colors\" icon=\"icon icon-eyedropper2\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Unlimited Colors for all Page Elements[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna supports full color management. You can set  a global Theme color that all your elements will inherit, you can then overwrite that color for specific page elements in order to style them differently. Most Fortuna elements allow color customizations: buttons, icons, icon boxes, bar graphs, counters, messages, lists etc. You also have full color control of your Header - manage your header background color/transparency, your navigation items color as well as their hover status color.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22830\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Google Fonts\" icon=\"icon icon-font\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Pick custom fonts for your Menus, Buttons, Headers &amp; Body[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna lets you have full control over your website fonts. Add any Google font then assign it to your Menus, Headings, Buttons, Body etc. You can also set the font-size, font-width, letter-spacing, font-weight etc for all your fonts globally.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22831\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Icon Sets\" icon=\"icon icon-thumbs-up\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" css_animation=\"\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]More than 1200 icons or 4 Premium Icon Sets[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna ships with <strong>4 Premium Icon Fonts</strong> that you can implement withing your page elements with the click of a button. Choose among more than <strong>1200 hot icons</strong> to add to your pages or implement within your Main Navigation, Icon boxes, Dividers, Buttons, Tab Navigations, Counters, Custom Slider Navigations etc. You can pick custom colors, styles, sizes for your icons as well in order to unleash your creativity and create unique content.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22834\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Unlimited Sidebars\" icon=\"icon icon-text2\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Unlimited Sidebars[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna lets you define an unlimited number of custom sidebars you can later assign to your pages. Add custom widgets to your sidebars like menus, Fortuna Latest News widget, Fortuna Contact widget, categories etc, pick a global sidebar position for your website and overwrite it voluntarily within each page.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22835\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Demo Data\" icon=\"icon icon-disk2\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Easy to import Demo Data[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna comes with Full Demo Data ready to import straight onto your Wordpress installation. All Revolution Slider Demos (Sliders) are also included so you can use them as a base for your own sliders.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22837\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Woocommerce Ready\" icon=\"icon icon-shopping-cart\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Full Woocommerce Support, start selling with Fortuna today![/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Create a WooCommerce online store in a matter of minutes &amp; start selling with Fortuna today! The theme also includes a few custom Modules for WooCommerce, custom sidebars for your store and product pages, a capability for adding a slider above your store, animated Ajax Cart in your website header etc.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22839\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22823\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Support &amp; Updates\" icon=\"icon icon-lifebuoy\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Fortuna ships with a 5-Star Support + Lifetime FREE updates[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Should you have any question or issue with Fortuna you can post it in our support forum and we will assist you shortly in a friendly and timely matter! Unlimited updates are also included with your ThemeForest purchase.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22841\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Translation Ready\" icon=\"icon icon-chat2\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Translation Ready[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna Worpress Theme follows good-coding practices with translation in mind and comes with Po/Mo files for English, that are ready for Internationalization and Translation.\nIt is also fully compatible with WPML plugin as well as qTranslate in case you wish to have a multi-language website.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22842\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"SEO Optimized\" icon=\"icon icon-search3\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]SEO Optimized[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna is written with SEO in mind! Headings, breadcrumbs, navigation, meta tags etc. and the way they appear in the code were taken under consideration when Fortuna templates were coded.\nFurthermore Fortuna is fully compatible with SEO Yoast plugin and recommends its use for a complete SEO solution on your website.[/vc_column_text][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_single_image image=\"22843\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"grey_border_img\"][/boc_tab][boc_tab title=\"Fully Documented\" icon=\"icon icon-bookmark\"][boc_heading html_element=\"h2\" alignment=\"left\" color=\"#333333\" subheading=\"\" background=\"bgr_multidotted\" margin_top=\"0px\" margin_bottom=\"20px\"]Fortuna is Fully Documented[/boc_heading][boc_spacing height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Fortuna\'s thorough Documentation takes your through the whole process of installing your theme, importing the Demo, creating pages, using the various elements and plugins, customizing the theme etc.[/vc_column_text][/boc_tab][/boc_tabs][boc_spacing height=\"40px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Features Overview','','publish','open','open','','features-overview','','','2015-05-22 13:05:16','2015-05-22 13:05:16','',0,'http://blueowlcreative.com/wp/fortuna_export/?page_id=22791',0,'page','',0),
